97
00:05:51,040 --> 00:05:52,920
Dia itu ibu kandungmu.

98
00:05:59,839 --> 00:06:00,760
Pelan-pelan.

99
00:06:01,239 --> 00:06:02,279
Hati-hati.

100
00:06:03,480 --> 00:06:06,480
Direktur Lin,
kau istirahat di mobil dulu.

101
00:06:06,760 --> 00:06:08,079
Kupanggil setelah tiba di rumah.

102
00:06:32,279 --> 00:06:33,920
Direktur Jiang,
mungkin mobilnya ada masalah.

103
00:06:33,920 --> 00:06:35,200
Tidak bisa dihidupkan.

104
00:06:35,399 --> 00:06:36,440
Bagaimana ini?

105
00:06:37,480 --> 00:06:39,160
Aku harus pergi bertemu Direktur Xu.

106
00:06:40,720 --> 00:06:41,799
Bagaimana jika naik mobil Direktur Lin?

107
00:06:41,799 --> 00:06:43,640
Tadi aku lihat dia
keluar bersama Direktur Jiang.

108
00:07:07,880 --> 00:07:10,839
Zhang, apa ponselmu yang berbunyi?

109
00:07:11,079 --> 00:07:12,160
Bukan.

110
00:07:25,600 --> 00:07:26,320
Direktur Lin.

111
00:07:26,799 --> 00:07:27,839
Boleh bicara?

112
00:07:28,880 --> 00:07:30,839
Direktur Yu memintaku menyampaikan…

113
00:07:31,040 --> 00:07:33,799
